snippet.title: Satama Puzzle Trailer
snippet.description:
▶Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1844680/

Satama Puzzle is a relaxing building and puzzle game where you will optimize the layout of a Port of Unloading. Each level will have three random variable scoring conditions, so it will be a new experience each time. Try to beat your score!

▶Twitter: https://twitter.com/mc2games
